00026 #ifndef DFAN_H  /* avoid re-inclusion */
00027 #define DFAN_H
00028 
00029 #include "hdf.h"
00030 
00031 #define DFAN_LABEL  0
00032 #define DFAN_DESC   1
00033 
00034 #define DFAN_LAB_BLKSIZE   64   /* default blksize to use for labels */
00035 #define DFAN_DESC_BLKSIZE 512   /* default blksize to use for descriptions */
00036 
00037 #define DFAN_DEFENTRIES 16  /* no of dir entries to add at a time */
00038 
00039 /*
00040  * This structure stores an entry in the label/desc directory
00041  * for a label/desc in the file, it gives the ref of the label/desc,
00042  * and the tag/ref of the data item to which the label/desc relates
00043  */
00044 typedef struct
00045   {
00046       uint16      annref;       /* ref of annotation */
00047       uint16      datatag;      /* tag of data */
00048       uint16      dataref;      /* ref of data */
00049   }
00050 DFANdirentry;
00051 
00052 /*
00053  * This structure is a head node for the directory, which is organized as
00054  * as a linked list of arrays.  DFANdirentry is the structure of an
00055  * array element, while DFANdirhead is the list element
00056  */
00057 typedef struct DFANdirhead
00058   {
00059       struct DFANdirhead *next; /* list element */
00060       int32       nentries;     /* Numer of entries */
00061       DFANdirentry *entries;  /* actually an arbitrary size array */
00062   }
00063 DFANdirhead;
00064 
00065 #endif /* DFAN_H */
